TITLE: Paginating Relay Connection with Preserved Filters
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to paginate a Relay connection while preserving the original filter values used in the initial query.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/relay/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-v16.0.0/guided-tour/list-data/refetching-connections.md#2025-04-18_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
