TITLE: Implementing Relay Network Layer with Fetch
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a basic Relay network layer using the fetch API to communicate with a GraphQL server. Demonstrates environment setup with network and store configuration, including a fetchQuery implementation that handles GraphQL operations.
