TITLE: Implementing Infinite Scrolling Newsfeed in GraphQL and React
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to implement an infinite scrolling newsfeed using Relay, including modifying the GraphQL query, creating a fragment for pagination, and using usePaginationFragment in the React component.
