TITLE: Implementing useQueryLoader in React
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates the use of the useQueryLoader hook from the react-relay package. The hook manages GraphQL queries by loading, retaining, and disposing of query references in a React component. It shows how to set up the useQueryLoader hook with an AppQuery and interact with it using loadQuery and disposeQuery callbacks. Dependencies include react-relay and preloaded GraphQL queries.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/relay/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-v13.0.0/api-reference/hooks/use-query-loader.md#2025-04-18_snippet_0

