TITLE: Refetching Fragment without Suspense using fetchQuery in React and Relay
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to refetch a fragment without triggering Suspense by using fetchQuery. It manually manages a loading state and ensures the data is cached before calling refetch with a 'store-only' fetch policy.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/relay/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-v14.0.0/guided-tour/refetching/refetching-fragments-with-different-data.md#2025-04-18_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
