TITLE: Using usePreloadedQuery with React Relay
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the usePreloadedQuery hook in conjunction with useQueryLoader to access preloaded query data in a React component. It shows how to manage the query lifecycle and display user data, including handling loading states via React's Suspense.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/relay/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-experimental/RelayHooks-ApiReference.md#2025-04-18_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
