TITLE: Implementing useTransition with Refetchable Fragments in React and Relay
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to use React's useTransition hook with Relay's useRefetchableFragment to improve the loading experience. By wrapping the refetch call in startTransition, the component can show a pending state while keeping the previous data visible instead of displaying a Suspense fallback during data loading.
