TITLE: Updating Multiple Filtered Connections in Relay
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to update multiple connection records when adding new edges, taking into account different filter conditions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/relay/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-v17.0.0/guided-tour/list-data/updating-connections.md#2025-04-18_snippet_14

