TITLE: Testing Relay Query Components with createMockEnvironment
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to test different states (Loading, Data Render, Error) of a Relay Query component using createMockEnvironment and MockPayloadGenerator. It shows how to simulate query resolution and rejection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/relay/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-v13.0.0/guides/testing-relay-components.md#2025-04-18_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
