TITLE: Adding an edge to a connection using updater function
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code snippet shows how to add an edge to a Relay connection inside an updater function. It retrieves the connection record, gets the payload from the server, and constructs the new edge using `ConnectionHandler.buildConnectionEdge` before adding it to the connection.
