TITLE: Using useEntryPointLoader in React
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the `useEntryPointLoader` hook in a React component to load and dispose of an EntryPoint. It uses a button to trigger the loading and disposal of the EntryPoint, and renders the EntryPoint's content using `EntryPointContainer` within a `Suspense` component.
