TITLE: Using useEntryPointLoader Hook with React and Relay
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to use the useEntryPointLoader hook to manage EntryPoint loading and disposal in a React component. Demonstrates integration with EntryPointContainer and handling of loading states.
