TITLE: Using useFragment Hook with GraphQL in a React Component
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use Relay's useFragment hook to fetch user data with a GraphQL fragment. The component receives a fragment reference as props and uses it to fetch the user's name and profile picture, then renders them in the UI.
