TITLE: GraphQL Schema Definition Snippet
DESCRIPTION: Provides part of a schema definition for a newsfeed app, illustrating GraphQL types and interfaces. Dependencies include a GraphQL server capable of processing schema definitions. Defines structure and relationships of data types like Story, Person, and Category. There are no direct inputs or outputs in this snippet.
