TITLE: Updating local data with commitLocalUpdate in Relay
DESCRIPTION: Updates the body and title fields of an existing Note record in the Relay Store using commitLocalUpdate.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/relay/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-v15.0.0/guides/client-schema-extensions.md#2025-04-18_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import {commitLocalUpdate} from 'react-relay';

function updateUserNote(environment, dataID, body, title) {
  commitLocalUpdate(environment, store => {
    const note = store.get(dataID);

    note.setValue(body, 'body');
    note.setValue(title, 'title')
  });
}
```

