TITLE: Updating GraphQL Connections with Conditional Logic in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows the procedure for conditionally updating GraphQL connections in Relay based on filter values. It involves determining whether a new comment should be added to a specific connection instance, for example, only adding comments made by friends to a 'friends-only' connection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/relay/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-v16.0.0/guided-tour/list-data/updating-connections.md#2025-04-18_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
