TITLE: RecordSourceSelectorProxy Interface Definition
DESCRIPTION: TypeScript interface definition for RecordSourceSelectorProxy, which provides methods to manipulate the Relay store.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/relay/blob/main/website/versioned_docs/version-v18.0.0/api-reference/relay-runtime/store.md#2025-04-18_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
interface RecordSourceSelectorProxy {
  create(dataID: string, typeName: string): RecordProxy;
  delete(dataID: string): void;
  get(dataID: string): ?RecordProxy;
  getRoot(): RecordProxy;
  getRootField(fieldName: string): ?RecordProxy;
  getPluralRootField(fieldName: string): ?Array<?RecordProxy>;
  invalidateStore(): void;
}
```

