TITLE: REST Response Caching Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Implements a basic URI-based response cache for REST requests using a Map.
SOURCE: https://github.com/facebook/relay/blob/main/website/docs/principles-and-architecture/thinking-in-graphql.md#2025-04-18_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
var _cache = new Map();
rest.get = uri => {
  if (!_cache.has(uri)) {
    _cache.set(uri, fetch(uri));
  }
  return _cache.get(uri);
};
```

